Document: VisualShaderNodeVec2Constant
Path: godot/classes/class_visualshadernodevec2constant.rst
Summary: Represents a constant Vector2 value used as an input in visual shader graphs.

Represents a constant Vector2 value used as an input in visual shader graphs. This node outputs a fixed Vector2 (x, y) value that can be connected to other nodes in a visual shader graph. The Vector2 value is defined in the node's parameters and remains unchanged during shader execution.
